They keep coming over to our side of town.

07:41.169 --> 07:42.534
Damn right.

07:44.047 --> 07:45.583
Those the same guys that got you?

07:47.801 --> 07:50.338
No. They were other guys.

07:50.512 --> 07:52.924
Now that I'm out,
I'm gonna make it my business

07:53.098 --> 07:55.305
