when I was in jail, man.

09:16.306 --> 09:19.264
It's cool. I'll see you guys later.

09:19.976 --> 09:21.841
- All right.
- See you later, Dal.

09:22.771 --> 09:24.887
Hey, Ponyboy, you got homework.

09:27.317 --> 09:29.273
You going home, Johnny Cade?

09:31.321 --> 09:33.357
I don't know.

09:33.531 --> 09:35.772
- See you around.
- All right.

09:59.599 --> 10:02.682
Turn off these lights
and get to bed.

10:02.852 --> 10:04.763
I got work in the morning.

10:06.731 --> 10:08.517
We leave them alone.

10:10.735 --> 10:12.225
I don't know.

10:12.403 --> 10:14.564
Who can figure it?

10:17.325 --> 10:20.408
- Are you cold, Pony?
- A little.

10:28.586 --> 10:30.167
Hey, listen, kiddo.

10:32.590 --> 10:34.501
Darry yells at you like that.

10:36.344 --> 10:37.925
He don't mean nothing.

10:39.139 --> 10:44.054
