was automechanics and gym.

11:08.251 --> 11:10.367
- You're not dumb.
- Yeah, I am.

11:12.213 --> 11:14.795
Hey, you shut up,
and I'll tell you something, though.

11:16.551 --> 11:19.338
You gotta promise me
that you're not gonna tell Darry.

11:19.512 --> 11:20.922
