- Leave her alone, Dal.

16:48.132 --> 16:51.716
That's the Greaser who just got out
of some jail or something.

16:51.886 --> 16:53.672
Yeah, sure. Whatever you say, honey.

16:53.846 --> 16:55.677
Leave us alone,
or I'll call the cops.

16:55.848 --> 16:58.681
Oh, my, my!
You got me scared to death!

16:58.851 --> 17:01.934
What am I,
what am I gonna do now, Pony, huh?

17:02.104 --> 17:04.060
