30:23.822 --> 30:25.938
What is Darry gonna say?

30:38.086 --> 30:41.078
Yeah, it's Darry.

30:41.256 --> 30:43.212
Yeah. Bye.

30:48.138 --> 30:50.880
Where the hell have you been?
