30:51.058 --> 30:53.140
It's two o'clock in the morning, kiddo.

30:53.310 --> 30:55.471
- Where have you been?
- I feel asleep in the lot.

30:55.645 --> 30:57.385
- You what?!
- I was talking to Johnny.

30:57.564 --> 31:00.101
And I fell asleep in the lot.
I didn't mean to.

31:00.275 --> 31:02.891
