- Look, I said I didn't mean to!

31:10.660 --> 31:13.493
"I didn't mean to!" "I forgot."
That's all I ever hear from you.

31:13.663 --> 31:16.700
- Come on, Darry...
- Tired of you sticking up for him!

31:16.875 --> 31:19.912
Don't you yell at him!

31:20.087 --> 31:22.874
Ponyboy! I didn't mean to!

31:37.813 --> 31:40.429
Come on, Johnny!
Move out of the way!

31:52.953 --> 31:56.821
Take it easy, Pony. It will be all right.
You just have to cool it, man.

31:56.998 --> 31:59.865
Got a cigarette, Johnny?
I'm scared to death.

32:00.043 --> 32:02.876
Well, don't be, man.
You're scaring me.

32:03.046 --> 32:05.833
- What happened?
- Darry hit me!

32:06.007 --> 32:08.623
I swear we used to get along fine
until Mum and Dad died.

32:08.802 --> 32:10.758
Now he can't stand me!

32:10.929 --> 32:13.466
I think I like it better
when the old man's hitting me.

32:13.640 --> 32:15.551
At least he knows I'm there.

32:17.936 --> 32:19.472
Let's walk to the park and back.

32:19.646 --> 32:21.978
Maybe I'll cool off enough to go home.

32:22.149 --> 32:25.892
Yeah, all right.
Ain't you about to freeze to death?

32:27.362 --> 32:29.023
You're ain't a' woofin'.

32:55.223 --> 32:56.633
Pony!

33:04.191 --> 33:06.022
Pony, got a light?

33:07.027 --> 33:09.063
Found this butt, man.

33:09.237 --> 33:11.569
Yeah, here you go, Johnny.

33:13.966 --> 33:15.402
Look what's coming.

33:15.994 --> 33:18.076
