33:18.246 --> 33:20.237
I bet they're looking for us.

33:24.085 --> 33:26.041
- Wanna split?
- Stay cool.

33:27.047 --> 33:31.882
Well, well, well.
What do you guys know?

33:32.052 --> 33:33.508
They're drunk.

33:36.681 --> 33:38.512
It's that guy with the rings, man.

33:38.683 --> 33:43.768
Aren't these the Greasers
who tried to pick up our women?

33:44.606 --> 33:47.313
You guys are out of your territory.
You better watch it.

33:47.484 --> 33:48.974
No, pal. You better watch it.

34:00.539 --> 34:02.871
You guys know what Greasers are?

34:03.041 --> 34:05.783
White trash with long greasy hair.

34:15.303 --> 34:17.793
- You know what a Soc is?
- What?

34:17.973 --> 34:20.965
White trash with Mustangs and madras.

34:21.141 --> 34:22.348
Get 'em!

34:29.234 --> 34:30.313
Johnny!

34:32.828 --> 34:34.313
Stay down, pal!

34:34.489 --> 34:35.603
Chuck him!

34:48.878 --> 34:51.369
Grab his arms! Right down!

34:55.217 --> 34:58.631
Did somebody get a drink
for this Greaser, huh?

34:58.805 --> 35:01.638
Come on! Have a drink, pal!

35:57.364 --> 36:00.731
I... I... I killed him.

36:04.496 --> 36:06.737
I killed that boy.

36:09.334 --> 36:10.744
I killed him.

36:20.428 --> 36:22.714
Johnny, I think I'm gonna be sick!

36:25.266 --> 36:27.973
Go ahead, man.
I ain't... I ain't gonna look at you.

36:28.144 --> 36:29.850
Ain't gonna look at you.

36:40.573 --> 36:43.064
Pony, are you all right?

36:46.413 --> 36:48.654
You really did kill 'em, huh, Johnny?

36:51.459 --> 36:53.040
Yeah.

36:56.089 --> 36:57.499
I had to.

36:59.217 --> 37:02.209
They, they were drowning you,
and they might have killed you!

37:06.683 --> 37:08.344
They were gonna beat me up!

37:10.145 --> 37:12.978
- What happened to the other guys?
- Huh?

37:16.109 --> 37:18.725
They... they all ran.
They all ran off.

37:18.903 --> 37:21.110
When I stabbed him, they all ran.

37:54.563 --> 37:55.554
What do you boys want?

37:55.732 --> 38:00.442
- Dally. W-w-w-we gotta see Dally.
- He's busy.

38:00.612 --> 38:04.070
Just tell him it's Ponyboy and Johnny, man!
He'll come!

38:05.909 --> 38:07.399
Come on!

38:25.553 --> 38:27.635
What do you guys want?

38:27.806 --> 38:30.513
- Johnny killed the Socs.
- What?

38:31.976 --> 38:34.433
All right. Good for you.
Let's go.

38:34.604 --> 38:37.141
We figured you could get us out,
if anyone could, Dal.

38:37.315 --> 38:40.899
I... I'm sorry I got you away
from this party and all,

38:41.069 --> 38:43.151
but I just don't know
what to do, man.

38:43.321 --> 38:45.027
I was just trying to get some sleep.

38:45.198 --> 38:47.154
I got into a fight with Shepard tonight.

38:47.325 --> 38:50.067
Let's see what we can do about this mess.
Get in.

38:50.245 --> 38:52.577
- Ponyboy, are you wet?
- Yeah, I'm OK.

38:56.501 --> 38:58.412
Hey, hey! Pony, come on, man.

38:59.629 --> 39:02.462
You'll die of pneumonia
before the cops ever get to you!

39:07.554 --> 39:09.465
Come on.

39:09.639 --> 39:12.756
